<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #e91e63;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8d7da;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ChezFlora</h1>
            <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) Request</p>
        </div>
        <p class="message">Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
        <p class="message">Use the following OTP to verify your email. This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>.</p>
        <p class="otp">{{otp}}</p>
        <p class="message">If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>ChezFlora &copy; 2024 | All Rights Reserved | Design, coded and Deployed by <a href="https://github.com/DimitriTedom" target="_blank">Dmitri Tedom (SnowDev)</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
